originalText.text:
The BEST Senior Center! The food is almost to die for! The activities, the outings, the wisdom, the services... I almost don't want to share this information, but it's just too good to keep to myself. It's not a put down of other centers, it's just that there's not another like this one!

These wonderful human beings are so caring, I have to force myself not to become emotional. A "regular" participant, bullied my Mom and I (we're new participants), yelling "This is my seat!..." Her fellow participants rallied in defense of my 81 year old mother and myself. Wow! All week long, people have approached us, telling us they heard what happened and are so CARING and supportive. Their care and concern causes my eyes to water; for I've never experienced such care, especially by so many strangers.

This makes me want to be a secret billionaire, so that I could surprise our "Angel Defenders" with a generous surprise üòâüòÅ!

We went to Walmart, with another senior center. We were on a bus and our groceries bags intermingled, in the bin below-yet- no one stole anyone else's bags. Just honest people, or else we all KNOW karma is real, or both üòÉ! I just LOVE this Center ‚ù§Ô∏èüòç
